{"tid":2374033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本女團成員被迫“下海”，一夜之間粉絲暴漲，收入比原來多十倍","createTime":"2021-01-21T02:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T03:23:28.000Z","uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a3bbfe3c6c38ac498a1ecdf539c79aac87ad575f","tid":2374033,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:36:12.000Z","msg":"女團在以前很吃香，在許多地方都受到追捧，尤其是日本，宅男人數多，女團經濟有很好的市場。不過隨著娛樂圈的更新換代，女團不再像從前那般輝煌，再加上成員們不願意自己被埋沒，想要成為唯一的女主角，因此很多人選擇了單飛。<br />\n<br />\n  此外，日本一直存在著不少地下偶像團體，她們名義上和藝人沒差別，實際上薪資和待遇要比普通工薪族還少。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0120%2Faf6da4dfj00qn8esy005ec000xc00p0g.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0120%252Faf6da4dfj00qn8esy005ec000xc00p0g.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=c1134dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  隨著疫情席捲而來，日本也面臨著嚴峻的經濟考驗，2020年度GDP增長達負的5.3%。受此情況影響，最開始支撐不住的，就是這些所謂的地下偶像團體，有被迫解散的，甚至有女團成員被迫&ldquo;下海&rdquo;，不得已和蒼老師（蒼井空）成為同行。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0120%2Fbd6597f6j00qn8esz0012c000et008cg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0120%252Fbd6597f6j00qn8esz0012c000et008cg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=c5048480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  有日本粉絲在推特爆料稱，發現自己喜歡的愛豆（偶像）脫離了之前的女團，竟然在女優圈子里活躍了起來，並且還在&ldquo;R級影片&rdquo;貨架上找到了她的片子。可想而知，看到偶像&ldquo;下海&rdquo;的那一刻，那位粉絲的內心是崩潰的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0120%2F6a2c9a76j00qn8esz0008c000d4003cg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0120%252F6a2c9a76j00qn8esz0008c000d4003cg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=8be62d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  消息一出，引來更多粉絲一片嘩然，無法接受曾經清純的愛豆轉變得如此之快。隨後，那名愛豆發推回應，表示網友們想查就查，但還請不要打擾她之前的團體成員和粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0120%2F5f76efb1j00qn8et0002kc000go009eg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0120%252F5f76efb1j00qn8et0002kc000go009eg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=ee04585f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  據悉，用戶名為&ldquo;八乙女&rdquo;的這個女生，是地下女團GIRL'S HORIZON的成員之一，她才剛滿19歲不久，原名叫高山さやか。<br />\n<br />\n  因為疫情影響，GIRL'S HORIZON已經很久沒有接到商業活動了，從去年5月份開始，她就呆在家裡休息。可是這一情況並沒有得到改善，由於缺少表演機會和薪酬，無奈之下只能選擇退團。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  理一下時間線，高山さやか在去年5月份休養生息，12月份宣布退團，退團後還不到兩個禮拜，粉絲們就驚訝地發現，她的名字出現在了另一成人影片領域，速度快得令人瞠目咋舌。<br />\n<br />\n  不過最諷刺的是，高山さやか在&ldquo;下海&rdquo;拍片後人氣反而急劇上升，比她在女團時期要輝煌得多。一夜之間粉絲暴漲，收入更是比原來多了數十倍，或許對她來說也算是一件好事吧。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0120%2F583a6d13j00qn8et0001wc000go00bhg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0120%252F583a6d13j00qn8et0001wc000go00bhg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=c5c97be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  其實不僅是高山さやか，早前也有一名與她經歷相似的日本女星被迫&ldquo;下海&rdquo;。和高山さやか一樣，&ldquo;南乃空&rdquo;之前也是地下女偶像，類似於中國小有名氣的網紅。<br />\n<br />\n  &ldquo;南乃空&rdquo;一開始是北都集團旗下的王牌公司MOODYZ的素人身份出道的，後來因為經濟不景氣，才被迫&ldquo;下海&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0120%2Fa8530769j00qn8et0001ac000d600bng.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0120%252Fa8530769j00qn8et0001ac000d600bng.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=51bb0693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  根據NHK電視台數據統計，在日本，有高達80%的偶像團體都是地下偶像，而地下偶像往往是最容易&ldquo;下海&rdquo;的團體。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  所謂&ldquo;地下偶像&rdquo;，她們大多數都隸屬於小事務所或者無事務所，甚至壓根就無人培養，自學出道。收益主要來源於跟粉絲的直接接觸，或者說粉絲在演唱現場買的東西，會根據不同情況對買東西的粉絲送出不同福利。<br />\n<br />\n  比如日本遊有一個叫做棉花糖3D+的組合，就是屬於地下偶像，她們每次表演結束後，就會發放價值人民幣120元的&ldquo;揉揉卷&rdquo;給粉絲購買，只要購買了之後就可以去觸摸組合成員。<br />\n<br />\n  即便如此，地下女團偶像獲得的收入依舊不高，跟明面上的真正明星是沒法比的。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0120%2Fab185177j00qn8et1001ac000k000jbg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0120%252Fab185177j00qn8et1001ac000k000jbg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=eb55a752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  日本電視台曾針對地下偶像拍攝過一個紀錄片，在《地下偶像的青春》紀錄片中，有些偶像還得靠種豆芽來節約開支，坐公交、趕地鐵、被剋扣薪資都是常有的事，比&ldquo;窮忙族&rdquo;還要困苦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0120%2F0c779dbej00qn8et30020c000k000b8g.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0120%252F0c779dbej00qn8et30020c000k000b8g.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=8771ec63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  她們只能靠自己強大的意志力支撐著，因為有夢想，所以期待著有一天也能成為&ldquo;正規軍&rdquo;。不過對於地下偶像而言，真正能從地下走到地上的永遠只是少數。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0120%2F9eaa6ae1j00qn8et2002gc000k000b9g.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0120%252F9eaa6ae1j00qn8et2002gc000k000b9g.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=16c5e224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  理想很美好，現實很骨感，夢想在殘酷的現實面前，一文不值。為了生計，已經越來越多地下偶像女團成員選擇&ldquo;下海&rdquo;。只能說，職業不分貴賤，至少是憑努力辛苦所得，並且在日本當女優也不是什麼見不得人的事，每個人選擇不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0120%2F99880de1j00qn8et3004wc0014000qhg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0120%252F99880de1j00qn8et3004wc0014000qhg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=9c0a612f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd5b776b781e0324d0e81a0f7000646150345263","tid":2374033,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a17c5b8edb681a8fc01ed71254ff7a330a58c37","tid":2374033,"uid":11254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"MIFD-140"},{"pid":"964238f2991f4640c6410dc105f76000b9392915","tid":2374033,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就嚟變月經po"},{"pid":"9158b3b678fad9295ffc6ed8266e309c683caafb","tid":2374033,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:50:56.000Z","msg":"有日本粉絲在推特爆料稱，發現自己喜歡的愛豆（偶像）脫離了之前的女團，竟然在女優圈子里活躍了起來，並且還在&ldquo;R級影片&rdquo;貨架上找到了她的片子。可想而知，看到偶像&ldquo;下海&rdquo;的那一刻，那位粉絲的內心是崩潰的。<br />\n<br />\n咩呀,睇唔起av呀"},{"pid":"1c3bf8e4f8a133c503dd89ed2a66754a2ee65ba0","tid":2374033,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a17c5b8edb681a8fc01ed71254ff7a330a58c37","tid":2374033,"uid":11254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"MIFD-140"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784a38cca7a326066cb4134bb61f8532b8a4e0d0","tid":2374033,"uid":171800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c3bf8e4f8a133c503dd89ed2a66754a2ee65ba0","tid":2374033,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a17c5b8edb681a8fc01ed71254ff7a330a58c37","tid":2374033,"uid":11254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"MIFD-140"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:54:04.000Z","msg":"Lm返屋企再睇真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a6f5986c44a163ed3d31cdf9afb2df24988528","tid":2374033,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1c3bf8e4f8a133c503dd89ed2a66754a2ee65ba0","tid":2374033,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a17c5b8edb681a8fc01ed71254ff7a330a58c37","tid":2374033,"uid":11254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"MIFD-140"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:55:15.000Z","msg":"條女幾正 幾似寶欣"},{"pid":"4e7564afc36dc713d21e147df168e5c372f179c1","tid":2374033,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"784a38cca7a326066cb4134bb61f8532b8a4e0d0","tid":2374033,"uid":171800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c3bf8e4f8a133c503dd89ed2a66754a2ee65ba0","tid":2374033,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a17c5b8edb68